ve board game library. Grab a game, play it over and over or come back and borrow another one!\n\nBUY: \nHoW have great range of games that you can purchase with your $5 discount. Buy a game on the night, rip the plastic off and play it then and there! Don\'t forget about the games library, if you play a game you like chances are you\'ll be able to grab a copy for your very own!\n\nSHARE: \nMany of the attendees love to share their board games. What better way to find people to play your games with than bringing them to games night? If you\'re happy to share your games, dump them on the game pile in the playing area but just make sure you know what\'s yours! If you\'re not into sharing no problem, just keep them with you and ask around for a game.\n\nFOOD: \nYou can buy drinks and snacks in store as well as a limited selection of hot food such as pies and sausage rolls. The House of War is also fully licensed and has a selection of beers and ciders for you to choose from. If you are planning on having a bit of drink then please consider public transport to take you home. \n\nIf you\'re after something a bit more then there\'s pizza just a couple of doors down and Macca\'s over the road. You\'re welcome to eat in store but please use the bins outside for the rubbish that you bring in.\n\nPARKING AND PUBLIC TRANSPORT: \nIf you\'re not lucky enough to get a park out front then there\'s loads of parking on Olive Grove or across the road at Coles Supermarket. HoW is only a short walk from Ringwood train station. Just turn left, cross Wantirna Rd. and follow Maroondah Hwy until you\'re almost at New St.\n\nFind us on Meetup: \nhttps://www.meetup.com/Ringwood-Saturday-Games/','02-16-2019  7:30 PM','HoW Board Game Night ‑ $5 entry','publish','HoW Board Game Night ‑ $5 entry','event','197'),(54,'3 Oakdale Road, Upwey VIC, Australia','9','13','02-17-2019','-37.903086','145.313091','ROADMAP',' 61 411 225 874','SAORI Premium Japanese Sauce','https://en-gb.facebook.com/events/21