rs we have. But it’s never enough.\n\nThat’s not working smart. It’s working hard.\n\nYou feel stuck and frustrated. You don’t have a clear pathway to take yourself out of the grind and into your dream of scaling the business so you can help more people, have financial freedom – and make a massive Impact.\n\nYou’re not alone, I’ve met and spoken with thousands of Entrepreneurial Business Owners about this challenge, many of you want to break free from the 1:1 client work and start creating online products and automated income but you simply don’t know how to go about it.\n\n\n\n\nThe Digital Product Blueprint Half-Day Workshop aims to get you on the path to business success by giving you the framework to build online programs and leverage your knowledge - even if you’ve never done this before.\n\nHaving additional programs to promote has so many benefits to you as a business owner and doesn’t need to be difficult, tiring or confusing.\n\nIt can be very simple.\n\nThis workshop is for Entrepreneurial Business Owners who want to take their business to the next level quickly – a much higher level – by harnessing the power of Digital Products.\n\n\n\n\nFrom it you will:\n\n- Become an expert in your niche\n\n- Automate your sales funnel\n\n- Increase your income\n\nIn the Digital Product Blueprint Half-Day Workshop, I’ll show you the proven formula that is going to transform your business in only a matter of weeks by teaching you the tricks of the trade, which even the greatest marketers don’t know, including Facebook Groups, Webinars and Teachable, plus a host of others. Yes, these are well-known platforms, but are you using them to your best advantage?\n\nReserve your ticket now and start creating automated products in your business. Every attendee will receive a copy of my book, \"Compelling Selling: How To Earn More By Selling Less\" absolutely FREE!\n\nMy clients are achieving huge success…one increased her income by 80% in 4 weeks!\n\nAnother extracted her knowledge to create a 3 tier $10K program, that she never knew it would be so simple to create.\n\nOthers have who have struggled with technology are shocked at how simple it is.\n\nWhile many have created additional resources to create a point of difference in their Target Market.\n\nThey have grown their businesses and the products they can offer to become credible experts and the go-to people in their industry. I used this formula myself when I started my business. At the time, I was fully booked with 1:1s, limited computer skills, had no list, no credibility, let alone have a network to leverage. But in 2 years I had created my Book, 2 Signature Online Programs, countless eBooks and Online Courses and 100s of webinars.\n\n\n\n\nThis workshop is for you if:\n\n1. You don\'t know how where to start, when it comes to going online.\n\n2. You are struggling to understand your point of difference within your expertise.\n\n3. You battle to convert those few leads because you don\'t know how to show them your massive value.\n\nLeveraging your knowledge and using my tried and trusted Digital Product techniques is how you create an endless supply of information products - whether you want to create: webinars, online courses, templates, pdfs, eBooks or memberships sites to generate more leads and automate your business success.\n\nIn the Digital Product Blueprint Half-Day workshop, you will:\n\n- Understand your target market, the importance of it and how to use it in your product creation. This is completely different to any “Ideal Client” you will learn.\n\n- Find out how to structure your online products so they naturally convert, without being salesy!\n\n- Learn how to be seen as the unicorn within a field of horses and uniquely stand out in your market.\n\n- Learn how to extract your knowledge and create an endless supply of online products, quickly and easily.\n\n- Build your email list and increase your network quickly.\n\n- Identify how to increase your revenue and nurtur